{"name":"Astute Defense","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You have a heightened sense of danger and can use your reflexes to dodge incoming blows. Starting at 6th level, when a creature you can see targets you with an attack, you can impose disadvantage on their attack roll as a reaction.</p><p>If the triggering attack misses, you can make one weapon attack against the attacker as part of the same reaction.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when a creature you can see targets you with an attack, you can impose disadvantage on their attack roll"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 6 (Investigator)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"astute%20defense_the%20savant_savant_investigator_savant_6_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"2282ecc797c9a3d595a8c9a9a54512e195e51b62"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496281,"modifiedTime":1682004496281,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"RCQYKx8ECMBUABKf"}
{"name":"Daring Determination","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You are well acquainted with dangerous situations. Starting at 6th level, the target of your Adroit Analysis cannot target you with opportunity attacks. Also, when a creature targets you with an opportunity attack, you can use your reaction to impose disadvantage on its attack roll.</p><p>In addition, when you are forced to make a saving throw to resist the effects of a trap, you gain a bonus to your roll equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of +1). If a trap allows you to take only half damage on a success, you instead take no damage if you succeed, and only half damage if you fail.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when a creature targets you with an opportunity attack, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 6 (Archaeologist)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"daring%20determination_the%20savant_savant_archaeologist_savant_6_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6313026793c07f8240856a5f8109384edeff1eb5"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496169,"modifiedTime":1682004496169,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"RLUp0nGCrOuESD1F"}
{"name":"Combat Medic","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You can administer aid in the midst of combat. Beginning at 3rd level, you can use an Action to use the following abilities:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \"><b>Adrenaline Jolt.</b> A creature you touch can immediately repeat a saving throw to end one of the following conditions: blinded, charmed, deafened, frightened, or poisoned, adding your Intelligence modifier (minimum of +1) to their roll.</li><li class=\"rd__li \"><b>Dress Wounds.</b> You touch a creature and expend an Intellect Die, immediately granting it temporary hit points equal to your Intellect Die roll + your Intelligence modifier.</li><li class=\"rd__li \"><b>Healing Surge.</b> A creature you touch can instantly expend one of its Hit Dice to regain hit points equal to its Hit Die roll + its Constitution modifier + your Intelligence modifier.</li><li class=\"rd__li \"><b>Stabilize.</b> You touch a living creature that has 0 hit points, automatically stabilizing them. The target can then choose to expend one of their Hit Dice to regain hit points equal to the maximum value of that Hit Die + their Constitution modifier.</li></ul></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 3 (Physician)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"combat%20medic_the%20savant_savant_physician_savant_3_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"58f838af4d8e155361bc1318d447c7d871c2a4b0"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496499,"modifiedTime":1682004496499,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"S58eZ9JAXTShHrsq"}
{"name":"Student of Truth","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>When you join this Academic Discipline at 3rd level, you gain proficiency in Insight and Investigation, and your proficiency bonus is doubled for any check you make with these skills. If you are already proficient in either skill you gain proficiency in another skill of your choice from the savant skill list.</p><p>You also have advantage on any ability check you make to detect illusions, shapeshifters, or if a creature is lying to you.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 3 (Investigator)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"student%20of%20truth_the%20savant_savant_investigator_savant_3_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"4bef9c7af04820daacdbc5c6cbe8036fefccc217"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496236,"modifiedTime":1682004496236,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"SzlZ9JmBUzhBLXnu"}
{"name":"Unarmored Defense","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Your observant style of fighting allows you to anticipate and dodge attacks. Starting at 1st level, when you are not wearing any armor or wielding a shield, your Armor Class is equal to 10 + your Dexterity modifier + your Intelligence modifier.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"unarmored%20defense_the%20savant_savant_1_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"5f3f2f74986ecf7da4031bc3f3200ac23ac697cb"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496714,"modifiedTime":1682004496714,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"TmiPutW74VsE3L4b"}
{"name":"Adroit Analysis","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 1st level, you can quickly analyze a foe's strengths and weaknesses. As a bonus action, you can Mark a creature you can see within 60 feet, gaining the following benefits for 1 minute or until you Mark another creature:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You can use Intelligence, in place of Strength or Dexterity, for your attack and damage rolls against that creature.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">If you hit the creature with an attack, or observe it for 1 minute, you learn one of the following characteristics of your choice: Armor Class, speed, one ability score, one of its senses, its maximum hit points, or its creature type.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on any Intelligence or Wisdom-based ability checks you make to analyze the creature. </li></ul><p>You can also use a bonus action to make an ability check using any Intelligence or Wisdom skill proficiency you have.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"adroit%20analysis_the%20savant_savant_1_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6cd7285024e97d9dc9e887c04d6c5594c7afc612"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496680,"modifiedTime":1682004496680,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"U1JVodNc3MgEBiC8"}
{"name":"Student of Medicine","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>When you join this Academic Discipline at 3rd level, you gain proficiency in Medicine and with herbalism kits, and your proficiency bonus is doubled for any check you make with either skill. If you are already proficient in either, you gain proficiency with another skill from the savant skill list.</p><p>Moreover, your studies grant you the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You can make Intelligence (Medicine) checks in place of any Wisdom (Medicine) checks you would make.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">If you spend at least 1 minute examining a creature, you can identify any disease, poison, or curse affecting it.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Once per turn, when you hit the target of Adroit Analysis with a weapon attack, you can reduce its speed by a number of feet equal to 5 times your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 5 feet) until the beginning of your next turn.</li></ul></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 3 (Physician)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"student%20of%20medicine_the%20savant_savant_physician_savant_3_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"41b4315f1f2ab5b17ff82630f576a3c1e9311681"}},"effects":[