{"name":"Master Investigator","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Your eye for the truth has reached near-supernatural levels. At 17th level, you gain Truesight in a 60-foot radius. Though, you cannot see into the Ethereal Plane within this range.</p><p>Also, when you, or a creature you can see, hits the target of your Adroit Analysis with a weapon attack, you can use your reaction to turn that attack into an automatic critical hit.</p><p>Once you use this reaction, you must complete a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when you, or a creature you can see, hits the target of your Adroit Analysis with a weapon attack, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 17 (Investigator)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"master%20investigator_the%20savant_savant_investigator_savant_17_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"be8405e9b6d655873edae8341a5f9faa4610449c"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496344,"modifiedTime":1682004496344,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"gNAlJm5Ub06vjRVe"}
{"name":"Academic Discipline","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 3rd level, choose an Academic Discipline: Archaeologist, Investigator, Naturalist, Physician, or Tactician, each of which is detailed at the end of this class description. Your Academic Discipline grants you features at 3rd level, and again at 6th, 13th, and 17th level in this class.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"academic%20discipline_the%20savant_savant_3_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"9fa8f53770ba4cea707ee2a7d9046439f9466df5"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496780,"modifiedTime":1682004496780,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"hG3tpJ2YcsnljCHl"}
{"name":"Ear to the Ground","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Your line of work has granted you a unique familiarity with the underbelly of the civilized world. At 6th level, you learn to speak, read, decode, decipher, and write in Thieves' Cant.</p><p>Also, once you spend a long rest in a settlement, you have advantage on any checks you make to gather information on that settlement, its culture, factions, or important figures.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 6 (Investigator)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"ear%20to%20the%20ground_the%20savant_savant_investigator_savant_6_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"8d58ebefaa0aecae0ecfc14e491c2981c2da6f95"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496300,"modifiedTime":1682004496300,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"i5nqd7ZfHgazilfL"}
{"name":"Perfect Recall","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You can recall picture-perfect details from things you commit to memory. Starting at 1st level, if you spend at least 1 minute observing something, you can recall any information about it, at any point in the future, without requiring an ability check.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"perfect%20recall_the%20savant_savant_1_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"948b53f3b46bb6283f0f8173726001a69b1f3b4e"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496696,"modifiedTime":1682004496696,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"iP6Y8vEppf3IKMpK"}
{"name":"Potent Observation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 2nd level, you can highlight your foe's weak points. As a reaction when a creature you can see hits the target of Adroit Analysis with an attack, you can increase the attack's damage by an amount equal to a roll of your Intellect Die.</p><p>When you reach 5th level, any attack that you make against the target of your Adroit Analysis can trigger this reaction.</p><p>Beginning at 11th level, this reaction increases the damage of the triggering attack by two rolls of your Intellect Die.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"potent%20observation_the%20savant_savant_2_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"8d90f008da954de7de34e32b00a1b52e26201477"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496760,"modifiedTime":1682004496760,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"infBDSgnsLy4LUId"}
{"name":"Undisputed Genius","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Upon reaching 20th level, you realize the true genius-level potential of your mind. Your Intelligence and Wisdom scores increase by 4. Your maximum for those scores is now 24.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"undisputed%20genius_the%20savant_savant_20_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"b29bf46d1fcc6c8a47b2a603117a92b8ed317916"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004497010,"modifiedTime":1682004497010,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"jurYaoSdUcMBeEG3"}
{"name":"Field Doctor","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You can move across the battlefield unscathed. Starting at 6th level, when you use your action to stabilize a creature, restore hit points, or grant temporary hit points, you gain the benefits of the Dodge action until the start of your next turn.</p><p>Additionally, when you use a Combat Medic action on your turn, you can make one weapon attack as a bonus action.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 6 (Physician)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"savant","hash":"field%20doctor_the%20savant_savant_physician_savant_6_savant","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"a0303359106e7bb7e114f9808894d5b0d1752d9b"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496517,"modifiedTime":1682004496517,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"kEnAuj5dvihF0sZ6"}
{"name":"Profound Insight","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You can predict attacks before they come to pass. Starting at 18th level, any creature marked by your Adroit Analysis has disadvantage on attack rolls they make against you, and you have advantage on any saving throw they force you to make.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"profound%20insight_the%20savant_savant_18_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"ddfe1f590ad076a67abb4f8d1fa78eef3b9b3bce"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496994,"modifiedTime":1682004496994,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"kRTv7UerTjvesgxf"}
{"name":"Accelerated Reflexes (2)","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>The speed at which you react to stimuli is incredible. Starting at 5th level, so long as you are not surprised, you add your Intelligence modifier (minimum of +1) to your initiative rolls.</p><p>You also gain one additional reaction you can take each round. A single effect can only trigger one of your reactions.</p><p>When you reach 17th level, your reflexes increase again, allowing you another reaction per round (for a total of 3).</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"The Savant 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"savant","hash":"accelerated%20reflexes%20(2)_the%20savant_savant_5_savant","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"5278773ab9d40c4c0c95a03555b66ab029dd6285"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004496799,"modifiedTime":1682004496799,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"n9uETv7bwiedB6xb"}
{"name":"Investigator","type":"subclass","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"mb-2 ve-flex-col\"><p><i class=\"ve-muted\">Note: importing a class as an item is provided for display purposes only. If you wish to import a class to a character sheet, please use the importer on the sheet instead.</i></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><div data-source=\"savant\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1598\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: The Savant\">Student of Truth</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>When you join this Academic Discipline at 3rd level, you gain proficiency in Insight and Investigation, and your proficiency bonus is doubled for any check you make with these skills. If you are already proficient in either skill you gain proficiency in another skill of your choice from the savant skill list.</p><p>You also have advantage on any ability check you make to detect illusions, shapeshifters, or if a creature is lying to you.</p></div><div data-source=\"savant\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1599\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: The Savant\">Rough &amp; Tumble</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>You have learned to fight dirty in the underbelly of the world. Beginning at 3rd level, your weapon attacks against the target of Adroit Analysis score a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20.</p><p>When you hit the target of Adroit Analysis with an attack, you can spend an Intellect Die and force the target to make a Constitution saving throw against your Investigator save DC:</p><p></p><div class=\"text-center\"><b>Investigator save DC</b> = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence modifier</div><p></p><p>On a failed save, it is blinded, deafened, or cannot speak (your choice) for 1 minute. It can repeat the saving throw at the start of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success.</p><p>When you score a critical hit, you use this feature without expending an Intellect Die, and the target has disadvantage on its initial Constitution saving throw.</p></div><div data-source=\"savant\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1600\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: The Savant\">Astute Defense</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>You have a heightened sense of danger and can use your reflexes to dodge incoming blows. Starting at 6th level, when a creature you can see targets you with an attack, you can impose disadvantage on their attack roll as a reaction.</p><p>If the triggering attack misses, you can make one weapon attack against the attacker as part of the same reaction.</p></div><div data-source=\"savant\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1601\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: The Savant\">Ear to the Ground</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>Your line of work has granted you a unique familiarity with the underbelly of the civilized world. At 6th level, you learn to speak, read, decode, decipher, and write in Thieves' Cant.</p><p>Also, once you spend a long rest in a settlement, you have advantage on any checks you make to gather information on that settlement, its culture, factions, or important figures.</p></div><div data-source=\"savant\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1602\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: The Savant\">Peerless Focus</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>Your gaze uncovers even the most well-hidden secrets and conspiracies. At 13th level, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">When you make an Intelligence (Investigation) or Wisdom (Insight) check you can treat a roll of 9 or lower as a 10.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You automatically detect and see through illusion spells cast at a level equal to your Intelligence modifier or lower.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Your weapon attacks against the target of Adroit Analysis score a critical hit on a roll of 18 through 20 on the d20.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Once per turn, you can choose to re-roll the damage from Potent Observation, but you must use the new roll.</li></ul></div><div data-source=\"savant\" class=\"rd__b refreshing-brew rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1603\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: The Savant\">Master Investigator</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>Your eye for the truth has reached near-supernatural levels. At 17th level, you gain Truesight in a 60-foot radius. Though, you cannot see into the Ethereal Plane within this range.</p><p>Also, when you, or a creature you can see, hits the target of your Adroit Analysis with a weapon attack, you can use your reaction to turn that attack into an automatic critical hit.</p><p>Once you use this reaction, you must complete a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"sav","identifier":"investigator","classIdentifier":"the-savant","advancement":[],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":""}},"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classes.